{"tid":2282401,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"漁護助理署長薛漢宗及親屬申請建丁屋 估值8千萬 12號截反對通知書","createTime":"2020-11-12T00:21:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-12T02:40:25.000Z","uid":242262,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"ef8fd651190ef1e76d44a1062183d4def19faee8","tid":2282401,"uid":242262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T00:21:20.000Z","msg":"【丁權】漁護署助理署長薛漢宗3年前在西貢大浪鹹田村申請興建丁屋，獲9千多封支持信惹公眾質疑。FactWire傳真社調查發現，本身是大浪原居民的薛漢宗及其親屬，近日已改為越村申請「飛丁」建屋，由偏遠的大浪改為到鄰近匡湖居的蠔涌村興建4間丁屋，建成後市價估值約8千萬元。<br />\n<br />\n記者於大浪的告示板找到地政總署有關建屋申請公告，諮詢期至明日(12日)截止，但公告並未見張貼於蠔涌村。蠔涌村村長對此表示全不知情。<br />\n<br />\n英文版本：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/35oNW4x\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F35oNW4x&d=J6hOlXozLSF63%2FYIn%2B2Au0wFe44qEnauMGuWilFD6Zg%3D&h=a80fc3dd\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/35oNW4x</a><br />\n足本報道：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2Io5nsT\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Io5nsT&d=J6hOlXozLSF63%2FYIn%2B2Au0wFe44qEnauMGuWilFD6Zg%3D&h=c93b32db\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2Io5nsT</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/396495580557502/posts/1601133120093736/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F396495580557502%2Fposts%2F1601133120093736%2F&d=J6hOlXozLSF63%2FYIn%2B2Au0wFe44qEnauMGuWilFD6Zg%3D&h=3e377429\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/396495580557502/posts/1601133120093736/</a>"},{"pid":"8aa3c63d579ed96b379b0f2f0e448ccef0e59219","tid":2282401,"uid":242262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T00:23:16.000Z","msg":"漁護高官及親屬「飛丁」蠔涌建4屋 明截反對書 村無公告村長稱不知情<br />\n<br />\n漁護署助理署長薛漢宗3年前在西貢大浪鹹田村申請興建丁屋，獲9千多封支持信惹公眾質疑。FactWire傳真社調查發現，本身是大浪原居民的薛漢宗及其親屬，近日已改為越村申請「飛丁」建屋，由偏遠的大浪改為到鄰近匡湖居的蠔涌村興建4間丁屋，建成後市價估值約8千萬元。記者於大浪的告示板找到地政總署有關建屋申請公告，諮詢期至明日(12日)截止，但公告並未見張貼於蠔涌村。蠔涌村村長對此表示全不知情。"},{"pid":"6b559c427d6848ea06451ffba400c7c215ff591e","tid":2282401,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T00:24:31.000Z","msg":"官官商衛"},{"pid":"0a4dffad1dd9de9ae3b5be104bf7031e1d270700","tid":2282401,"uid":242262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T00:24:39.000Z","msg":"漁護署助理署長薛漢宗3年前在西貢大浪鹹田村申請興建丁屋，獲9千多封支持信惹公眾質疑。FactWire傳真社調查發現，本身是大浪原居民的薛漢宗及其親屬，近日已改為越村申請「飛丁」建屋，由偏遠的大浪改為到鄰近匡湖居的蠔涌村興建4間丁屋，建成後市價估值約8千萬元。記者於大浪的告示板找到地政總署有關建屋申請公告，諮詢期至明日(12日)截止，但公告並未見張貼於蠔涌村。蠔涌村村長對此表示全不知情。<br />\n根據地政總署認可鄉村範圍地圖，西貢大浪包括4條村，分別為大浪村、大灣、林屋圍及鹹田村。地政總署上月底於大浪的鄉村告示板貼出3張建屋申請及收集反對意見的公告，內容顯示大浪村7名居民計劃在蠔涌村不同地點興建丁屋。其中一張公告是薛漢宗與另外3人薛漢輝、薛漢發及薛漢明，申請在蠔涌村附近，丈量約份244約地段第1945號A分段第14至17小分段(DD244 Lot 1945 SA Ss14-17)，興建合共4間丁屋。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xekCtba.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxekCtba.jpg&h=1848ebeb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e3fad6d99b232d3be0ac540fea5cddecfc9de08f","tid":2282401,"uid":242262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T00:26:36.000Z","msg":"公告日期為10月29日，並列明任何人如反對相關申請，反對書必須於11月12日或之前送達，逾期概不受理。不過記者現場視察，申請建屋的蠔涌村內，包括蠔涌新村南邊圍路、蠔涌村小巴站及蠔涌南邊圍的告示板，均不見貼有上述申建丁屋的公告，村民難以得知相關申請的詳情以提出反對。而目前張貼公告的西貢大浪與蠔涌村相距甚遠，以Google Earth量度，兩村直線距離超過14公里。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N9YAeRP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN9YAeRP.jpg&h=d72802de&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"04027e92a293c9e38867621426d3e5b59a0b73f1","tid":2282401,"uid":64576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T00:29:15.000Z","msg":"邊到有得寫信反對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74709734793c15675d7dc4a1f94796e101a98e3c","tid":2282401,"uid":223428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T00:29:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37f9e079cfe4ea3f9531711b2c07c498802cdd37","tid":2282401,"uid":116509,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T00:40:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e1f118c68614de55268ef2b0cb8ef883a7a0df3","tid":2282401,"uid":117301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T00:45:29.000Z","msg":"到底政府仲有邊個部門既官係正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36c9b4e42766a964d1dca79a9e578077554141a0","tid":2282401,"uid":28432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T00:46:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6362df492fc408bc76b29d537d5cb7860eb595bf","tid":2282401,"uid":54800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T01:14:19.000Z","msg":"薛漢宗「飛丁」！！"},{"pid":"862c1e479871b2077655293204293eb49b12d0bd","tid":2282401,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T01:15:59.000Z","msg":"隨時條村都冇9000人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c6a1d8af6f3ff6ee52b6b124754f3ff2b7707ea","tid":2282401,"uid":153811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T01:17:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1d2a66c2ceb260603044abd91168d94f73db310","tid":2282401,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T02:31:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4318e52815e3840bb78cb020617c8c027d31ab55","tid":2282401,"uid":6103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T02:40:25.000Z","msg":"又係地政總署<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}